    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "my project need this 'show more' link as well, defintely a must have>\nIn the same range of idea, a input filter, kind of auto-complete, would help the user to find his filter as well. \nSo i imagine an input text ( hidden per default) where the user can 'search' in the facet list directly instead of clicking 10 times on the 'show more' link to find his value.\nYes in my scenario, we have a lots of possilbie filter values (up to 36 000 for the projects for example)\nhence the requirements.\n\ndoes it makes sense ?\n",
